dcterms:description: The Yorùbá Bible is a modern translation of the Bible in the Yorùbá language, used to create parallel data with the English NIV Bible.
dcterms:title: Yorùbá Bible (Bíbélì Mímó ní Èdè Yorùbá Òde-Òní)

dcterms:description: The New International Version (NIV) English Bible is a widely used modern English translation of the Bible, utilized for creating parallel data with the Yorùbá Bible.
dcterms:title: New International Version (NIV) English Bible
